{"html":"<h2>Tactic(s)</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: coins<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: C<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;!St_C_1&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;!Bank_Pk&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;\\(last&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;splitEqs&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;Mint&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;~~&gt;&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;!KU\\(~r&quot;</p><br/>\n","title":"Tactics"}